snippet.title: Super-Easy Rocky Road Fudge
snippet.description: Rich and truly divine fudge! The easy way is the microwave method. This Rocky Road Fudge is a delicious mixture of chocolate chips, sweetened condensed milk, marshmallows and walnuts. It is easy to make and perfect to bring to all of your holiday parties!

snippet.title: Original NESTLÉ® TOLL HOUSE® Chocolate Chip Cookies
snippet.description: This famous classic American cookie is a treat no matter what the age or occasion. Enjoy it with a glass of cold milk.

snippet.title: Spring S'Mores Bars
snippet.description: Spring S'Mores Bars are colorful and delicious. These make a colorful springtime or Easter treat, but also are perfect for year-round entertaining.

snippet.title: Fusilli with Blue Cheese & Toasted Walnuts
snippet.description: Fusilli with Blue Cheese & Toasted Walnuts is high in flavor and quick to prepare. The blue cheese and walnuts add flair to this exquisite pasta dish.

snippet.title: Sea-Salted Smoky Almond Chocolate Bark
snippet.description: Sea-Salted Smoky Almond Chocolate Bark is a true treat for the more sophisticated palate. With the perfect mix of salty and sweet this chocolate bark is a unique dessert that is sure to impress.

snippet.title: Choc-Oat-Chip Cookies
snippet.description: These delicious favorite Choc-Oat-Chip Cookies are perfect for dessert or a snack. Filled with tasty oats and chocolate!

snippet.title: Easy Rocky Road Brownies
snippet.description: The enduring appeal of rocky road is no surprise. The combination of marshmallow, chocolate and nuts in these brownies is hard to resist.

snippet.title: Chocolate Oatmeal Chippers
snippet.description: Chocolate Oatmeal Chippers make a tasty and fun surprise in a lunch box and they take less than 30 minutes to prepare.

snippet.title: Sweet Potato Pies
snippet.description: These delicious Sweet Potato Pies have nutmeg and cinnamon flavors. These are a great addition to your pie collection. Everyone will be asking for more!

snippet.title: Chunky Chocolate Pecan Bars
snippet.description: These easy-to-make Chunky Chocolate Pecan Bars are ready in less than 1 hour. Perfect solution for snacks or entertaining.
